<ext_description linkend="Basic_geometry_arm.Vector">
A <b>Vector</b> is a type of <express_ref linkend="Elemental_geometric_shape:arm:Elemental_geometric_shape_arm.Detailed_geometric_model_element"/>. A 
<b>Vector</b> is a quantity that has magnitude and direction and that is commonly represented by a directed line 
segment whose length represents the magnitude and whose orientation in space represents the direction.
